Weixin::Client v1.0
========================
使用Perl语言编写的微信客户端，手机扫码登录

支持发送和接收好友消息、群组消息，支持和手机客户端同时在线

INSTALLATION:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES:
   
    JSON
    AnyEvent::HTTP
    LWP::UserAgent
    LWP::Protocol::https

